assetProfile.longBusinessSummary: Identi Healthcare Ltd provides healthcare inventory management systems. It offers Snap & Go, an image recognition technology to record medical implants and consumables used during surgery; RFID SmartCabinet, an automated inventory system developed to helps cath labs, neurosurgery, ophthalmology, EP labs, orthopedics, plastic surgery, gastro, and other; and Narcotics Cabinet, an automated system for the administration of controlled substances and narcotics. The company also provides Kanban & PAR solutions, including Smart Weighing Bin, a wireless and autonomous smart scale bin that re-orders its own supplies; Stock Pick, a solution that counts units taken and triggers an automatic order after reaching a level; Restock Tag, a solution that automatically replenishes inventory by clicking a button; and Scan & Restock, a mobile App to order and monitor orders. In addition, it offers IDENTIPlatform, a cloud based platform powered by artificial intelligence and machine learning that connects suppliers to hospitals; and gas cylinder stock management and curtain disinfection and cleaning services. The company is headquartered in Netanya, Israel.
